Attributes - Volumetric Clouds On/Off Op.Description: Performance (Off - Disable if your GPU still struggles with clouds when at the 4 major planets of stanton, this will load the old 2D clouds)
Recommended (On - Recommended for VR, aliasing on distant objects.)
Quality (On - Raises quality on distant objects slightly)
EXTREME (On - Best quality at the cost of lots of performance even on modern hardware)
